window.docContents[83].resolve({"/Type-______/____________/#mutual-inductive-types-same-parameters":{"contents":"mutual 组中的所有归纳类型必须具有相同的 参数。\n它们的指数可能不同。\n\nDiffering numbers of parameters尽管 Both 和 OneOf 不是相互递归的，但它们是在同一 mutual 块中声明的，因此必须具有相同的参数：mutual\n  inductive Both (α : Type u) (β : Type v) where\n    | mk : α → β → Both α β\n  inductive Optional (α : Type u) where\n    | none\n    | some : α → Optional α\nend\nInvalid mutually inductive types: `Optional` has 1 parameter(s), but the preceding type `Both` has 2\n\nNote: All inductive types declared in the same `mutual` block must have the same parameters\n\n\nDiffering parameter types尽管 Many 和 OneOf 不是相互递归的，但它们是在同一 mutual 块中声明的，因此必须具有相同的参数。\n它们都只有一个参数，但 Many 的参数不一定与 Optional 的参数位于同一宇宙中：mutual\n  inductive Many (α : Type) : Type u where\n    | nil : Many α\n    | cons : α → Many α → Many α\n  inductive Optional (α : Type u) where\n    | none\n    | some : α → Optional α\nend\nInvalid mutually inductive types: Parameter `α` has type\n  Type u\nof sort `Type (u + 1)` but is expected to have type\n  Type\nof sort `Type 1`\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009Type System\u0009归纳类型\u0009相互归纳类型\u0009要求","header":"4.4.5.1.2. 参数必须匹配","id":"/Type-______/____________/#mutual-inductive-types-same-parameters"},"/____________/_______________/#zh-notationsmacros-syntaxdef-h003":{"contents":"许多命名类型与解析器生成的基本标记相关联。\n通常，单令牌语法产生式由包含单个 atom 的 node 组成；节点中保存的种类允许识别该值。\n解析器不会解释文字的原子：字符串原子包括其前导和尾随双引号字符以及其中包含的任何转义序列，并且十六进制数字保存为以 \"0x\" 开头的字符串。\n提供 Helpers（例如 Lean.TSyntax.getString）来按需执行此解码。\n\n\n\nThe pseudo-kind assigned to identifiers: `ident.The name `ident is not actually used as a kind for Syntax.node values. It is used by\nconvention as the kind of Syntax.ident values.\n\n`str is the node kind of string literals like \"foo\".\n\n`interpolatedStrKind is the node kind of an interpolated string literal like \"value = {x}\"\nin s!\"value = {x}\".\n\n`interpolatedStrLitKind is the node kind of interpolated string literal\nfragments like \"value = { and }\" in s!\"value = {x}\".\n\n`char is the node kind of character literals like 'A'.\n\n`num is the node kind of number literals like 42 and 0xa1\n\n`scientific is the node kind of floating point literals like 1.23e-3.\n\n`name is the node kind of name literals like `foo.\n\n`fieldIdx is the node kind of projection indices like the 2 in x.2.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009符号和宏\u0009定义新语法","header":"23.4.3. 令牌和文字类型","id":"/____________/_______________/#zh-notationsmacros-syntaxdef-h003"}});